@startuml REQ-0030_Control_Loop_Processing
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "User" as User
entity "Mobile" as Mobile

box "IoT Library" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
  participant "Controller" as Controller
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
  participant "Event Bus" as Event_Bus
end box

header
  **REQ-0030: Control Loop Processing**
  //Description:// Process sensor data against thresholds and dispatch control\nactions. Report status via comm manager.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Controller_OnSensorData evaluates thresholds.\nController_ReportStatus sends status via Comm_SendStatus.
end header


Sensor_Driver --> Controller: EVENT_SENSOR_DATA_READY
Comm_Manager --> Controller: EVENT_CONTROL_ACTION
== Controller_OnSensorData() ==
note right of Controller: Threshold Check
Controller --> Controller: EVENT_CONTROL_ACTION
== Controller_Init() ==
Controller -> Event_Bus: Event_register(EVENT_SENSOR_DATA_READY, Controller_OnSensorData)
Controller -> Event_Bus: Event_register(EVENT_CONTROL_ACTION, Controller_ReportStatus)
== MsgBus_Init() ==
Controller -> Event_Bus: Event_register(EVENT_MSG_QUEUED, MsgBus_ProcessQueue)
== MsgBus_QueueInbound() ==
Controller --> Controller: EVENT_MSG_QUEUED
== Controller_ReportStatus() ==
Controller -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus(&status)
== MsgBus_ProcessQueue() ==
note right of Controller: Msg Dispatch Cycle
Controller -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus(&status)

@enduml